00:46:48.110 --> 00:46:54.300 align:middle line:90%


00:46:54.300 --> 00:46:56.430 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: That does have
some kind of a meditation

00:46:56.430 --> 00:46:57.780 align:middle line:90%
feel to it, doesn't it?

00:46:57.780 --> 00:47:00.560 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: Oh, it does.

00:47:00.560 --> 00:47:01.360 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:47:01.360 --> 00:47:02.980 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It puts you
in a different state.

00:47:02.980 --> 00:47:03.854 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: It does.

00:47:03.854 --> 00:47:06.040 align:middle line:84%
I highly recommend people
listen through headphones,

00:47:06.040 --> 00:47:08.030 align:middle line:90%
that has even more power.

00:47:08.030 --> 00:47:11.250 align:middle line:10%
But I mean just hearing that
little bit through speakers

00:47:11.250 --> 00:47:15.670 align:middle line:10%
to me it just obviously drives
something in my own conscious

00:47:15.670 --> 00:47:17.450 align:middle line:10%
whereas you start to
shape your whole mind

00:47:17.450 --> 00:47:21.120 align:middle line:10%
and consciousness with this
and it's very, very powerful.

00:47:21.120 --> 00:47:22.850 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Eben, it's
always enlightening

00:47:22.850 --> 00:47:24.950 align:middle line:84%
to talk with you
about your experience

00:47:24.950 --> 00:47:27.580 align:middle line:90%
and I'm glad you're here.

00:47:27.580 --> 00:47:30.260 align:middle line:84%
And there's no rush to
get to the other side,

00:47:30.260 --> 00:47:32.410 align:middle line:84%
but at least when you do
you've kind of given us

00:47:32.410 --> 00:47:35.336 align:middle line:84%
a little hint on what we
can expect, so thank you.

00:47:35.336 --> 00:47:37.460 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: Well, thank
you so much for having me.

00:47:37.460 --> 00:47:39.560 align:middle line:84%
It's always a joy
to be with you, too.

00:47:39.560 --> 00:47:42.610 align:middle line:84%
And you're doing a great
job waking this world up.

00:47:42.610 --> 00:47:45.890 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Dr. Eben
Alexander, "Map of Heaven,"

00:47:45.890 --> 00:47:49.070 align:middle line:84%
"Proof of Heaven,"
literally study guides

00:47:49.070 --> 00:47:53.690 align:middle line:84%
on what you can expect when you
cross over to the other side.

00:47:53.690 --> 00:47:56.880 align:middle line:10%
And as we've talked about,
there's no rush to get there

00:47:56.880 --> 00:48:00.010 align:middle line:10%
but when that day happens,
I think you'll be prepared.

00:48:00.010 --> 00:48:04.000 align:middle line:10%
I'm George Noory and thanks
for watching "Beyond Belief."

